{"title":"2019-12-29","virtualPath":"/Diary/","html":"<p>キラキオン。個体値が…</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2019/2019-12-29/20191229-190511-Screenshot_20191229-190511.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2019/2019-12-29/20191229-190511-Screenshot_20191229-190511.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>でも、とりあえずマックス強化。キラはやはり正義。しかし CP でみるとバンギよりも大部下なんだね。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2019/2019-12-29/20191229-223013-Screenshot_20191229-223013.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2019/2019-12-29/20191229-223013-Screenshot_20191229-223013.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>氷見から自転車で観音崎まで。あの街道は、「立山」という言葉に尽きる。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2019/2019-12-29/20191229-114246-P_20191229_114246_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2019/2019-12-29/20191229-114246-P_20191229_114246_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>氷見総湯に入るつもりだったけど、キラ交換できるという連絡がついたので回転寿司ちょっとだけつまんで氷見を離脱。氷見の寒ブリは正義。寒ブリはいいんだけど、この寿司屋は…</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2019/2019-12-29/20191229-183005-P_20191229_183005_1_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2019/2019-12-29/20191229-183005-P_20191229_183005_1_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>intel が死んでる。</p>\n","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"日記","updated":"2020-07-12T02:55:24","published":"2020-07-12T02:55:24"}